Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.48,0:22:58.69,Family Main,,0,0,0,,РЎф Not one of us are siblings РЎф
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.69,0:23:01.19,Family Main,,0,0,0,,РЎф We don't share any blood РЎф
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.57,0:23:05.91,Family Main,,0,0,0,,РЎф But our crew is still FAMILY! РЎф
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.29,0:23:14.66,Family Main,,0,0,0,,РЎф Survey maps galore, РЎф
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.66,0:23:19.21,Family Main,,0,0,0,,{\q2}РЎф The biggest maps you've ever laid your eyes on РЎф
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.21,0:23:21.92,Family Main,,0,0,0,,РЎф It wouldn't matter anyway, РЎф
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.92,0:23:24.67,Family Main,,0,0,0,,РЎф You'll never find family like this РЎф
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.67,0:23:29.47,Family Main,,0,0,0,,РЎф Only outstanding slackers and misfits РЎф
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.47,0:23:33.10,Family Main,,0,0,0,,РЎф Can come aboard our MOTHER SHIP РЎф
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.10,0:23:37.02,Family Main,,0,0,0,,РЎф Forsake all reason, then maybe РЎф
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.02,0:23:41.15,Family Main,,0,0,0,,РЎф You can sail along with us РЎф
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.94,0:23:46.53,Family Main,,0,0,0,,РЎф EVERYDAY ride out the storm РЎф
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.53,0:23:50.28,Family Main,,0,0,0,,РЎф That's all we can ask for РЎф
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.28,0:23:54.12,Family Main,,0,0,0,,{\q2}РЎф We'll find the greatest treasure, it's our quest, РЎф
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.12,0:24:00.29,Family Main,,0,0,0,,РЎф with the aid of our MOTHER SHIP РЎф
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.42,0:24:05.22,Family Main,,0,0,0,,РЎф The best people share a quirk, yeah РЎф
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.22,0:24:11.47,Family Main,,0,0,0,,РЎф They can laugh like no one else can! РЎф
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.43,0:24:14.56,Family Main,,0,0,0,,РЎф We're more than just companions РЎф
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.56,0:24:16.64,Family Main,,0,0,0,,РЎф Beyond what you would call friends РЎф
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.90,0:24:21.86,Family Secondary,,0,0,0,,РЎф While there's fun and we're free! РЎф
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.64,0:24:20.06,Family Main,,0,0,0,,РЎф We're each other's own FAMILY! РЎф
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.06,0:24:22.02,Family Main,,0,0,0,,РЎф Not one of us are siblings, РЎф
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.02,0:24:25.03,Family Main,,0,0,0,,РЎф We don't share any blood РЎф
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.03,0:24:29.32,Family Main,,0,0,0,,РЎф But our crew is still FAMILY! РЎф
